de.tub.reader.file
Class IterativeFileReader

java.lang.Object
  de.tub.observer.Subject
      de.tub.reader.file.IterativeFileReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFileReader, IReader, Cloneable
public class IterativeFileReader
extends Subject
implements IFileReader, Cloneable

This Reader reads all files in the given directory line by line and delegates the processing of each line to the given Processor. The files to read can be specified with an instance of FileFilter. The default behavior is to read all files in the given directory.

Author:
Sebastian Oelke
